The paper studies competitive diffusion games on graphs, which can be categorized as a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and social networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the existence of Nash equilibria on different classes of graphs, which involves graph theory (cs.DM) and control systems (cs.SY).
